abstract: >-
  Pro Worker AI (PWA) is a personalized AI augmentation layer that
  transforms how AI interacts with knowledge workers. Instead of
  treating users as generic recipients of AI output, PWA assesses
  expertise, goals, and work patterns to calibrate every AI interaction
  — coaching in growth areas, accelerating in expert domains, automating
  mechanical tasks, and protecting skills at risk of atrophying.
  Built on research by Buçinca (cognitive forcing, contrastive
  explanations), Acemoglu (complementarity economics), Mollick
  (productivity effects), and Drago & Laine (Intelligence Curse).
  Implemented as an MCP server with 13 tools for cross-platform
  portability across Claude, ChatGPT, Cursor, and custom agents.
